snippet.title: Off-Score Project: Elephants Remember - release trailer
snippet.description:
Off-Score's second interactive track: Elephants Remember is now available on Itch.io!  
https://offscore.itch.io/elephants-remember

You can also buy to the whole music album on Bandcamp! 
https://yentinglo.bandcamp.com/album/off-score/

🚗💨🐘🐘🐘

Off-Score Project, a music album that you can interact with.
http://offscoreproject.com

In #OffScore, a track is both a SONG written and performed by YenTing Lo and a GAME developed by Ferran Bertomeu and Vanja Mrgan. 


Follow us to stay tuned: 
🎮 Twitter：https://twitter.com/offscoreproject
🖊️ Subscribe mail list：https://bit.ly/2NuKxr7

#InteractiveMusicAlbum #gamerelease #musicrelease
